Company Overview of Lawrenceville Plasma Physics, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Lawrenceville Plasma Physics, Inc., doing business as LPPFusion, operates as a research and development company that works on environmentally clean Focus Fusion technology. It focuses on developing an energy source based on aneutronic fuels and the dense plasma focus device, a combination called Focus Fusion. Lawrenceville Plasma Physics, Inc. was founded in 1974 and is based in Middlesex, New Jersey.


